WEBVTT

00:00:29.375 --> 00:00:32.792
That adversity can have lasting effects.

00:00:34.167 --> 00:00:37.184
When I began to have
opportunities to speak

00:00:37.208 --> 00:00:40.518
and advocate for students
and for teachers,

00:00:40.542 --> 00:00:43.768
I found myself uniquely positioned

00:00:43.792 --> 00:00:46.750
to be able to speak
about childhood trauma.

00:00:47.583 --> 00:00:49.976
But I had to make a decision first.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:51.768
I had to decide,

00:00:51.792 --> 00:00:55.351
did I want to just share
the bright and shiny parts of my life,

00:00:55.375 --> 00:00:58.309
you know, those ones
that we put out on social media

00:00:58.333 --> 00:01:01.018
that make us all look perfect,